<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>18</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">章伟文著：《宋元道教易学初探》，第<font face="Times New Roman">126</font><font face="宋体">页，巴蜀书社，</font><font face="Times New Roman">2005</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">12</font><font face="宋体">月第</font><font face="Times New Roman">1</font><font face="宋体">版。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
